trans-unit.source: Defines the template of the final step for creating a user account with the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: 定義以 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 控制項建立使用者帳戶的最終步驟範本。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> class is derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep> and used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
By default the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> step is displayed after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step.
trans-unit.target: 根據預設<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep>步驟後，就會看到<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep>步驟。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> step is a required step of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep>步驟是必要的步驟的<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>控制項。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of user interface (UI) to display for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> page of a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定顯示 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> 控制項之 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 網頁的使用者介面 (UI) 型別。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete" /> enumeration value for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType" /> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete" /> 列舉型別的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType" /> 列舉型別值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property specifies the type of navigation UI to display for the final user account creation step (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step) of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A>屬性指定的導覽 UI 以顯示最終使用者帳戶建立步驟類型 (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep>步驟) 的<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>控制項。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to ensure that <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> is always set to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete> value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A>屬性覆寫<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性以確保<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep>一定會設定為<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete>值<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType>列舉型別。

trans-unit.source: Attempting to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property to a different value will result in an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 嘗試設定<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A>屬性設為不同的值將會導致<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性無法由佈景主題或樣式表主題設定。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> and [ASP.NET Themes and Skins](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute>和[ASP.NET 佈景主題和面板](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3)。

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to set the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType" /> property.
Gets or sets the title to display for the final user account creation step of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 控制項之使用者帳戶建立最終步驟的顯示標題。

trans-unit.source: The title to use for the final user account creation step of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: 此標題是使用於 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 控制項的使用者帳戶建立最終步驟。

trans-unit.source: The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性的值設定時，可以自動儲存到資源檔使用設計工具。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute> and [Globalization and Localization](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8ef3838e-9d05-4236-9dd0-ceecff9df80d).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute>和[全球化和當地語系化](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8ef3838e-9d05-4236-9dd0-ceecff9df80d)。
